                            <comment id="15970749" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 17 Apr 2017 06:58:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user WangTaoTheTonic opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/3727&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/3727&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6312&quot; title=&quot;Update curator version to 2.12.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-6312&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-6312&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;update curator version to 2.12.0 to avoid potential block&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    As there&apos;s a Major bug(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CURATOR-344&quot; title=&quot;SharedValue watcher should limit work to valid data change events &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CURATOR-344&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CURATOR-344&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CURATOR-344&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CURATOR-344&lt;/a&gt;)) in curator release used by flink, we need to update the release to 2.12.0 to avoid potential block in flink.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     (flink use recipes in checkpoint coordinator and we have already occurred problem in zookeeper failover when we&apos;re trying to fix &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6174&quot; title=&quot;Introduce a leader election service in yarn mode to make JobManager always available&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-6174&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-6174&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6174&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6174&lt;/a&gt;))&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can merge this pull request into a Git repository by running:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    $ git pull &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/WangTaoTheTonic/flink&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/WangTaoTheTonic/flink&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6312&quot; title=&quot;Update curator version to 2.12.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-6312&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-6312&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Alternatively you can review and apply these changes as the patch at:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/3727.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/3727.patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To close this pull request, make a commit to your master/trunk branch&lt;br/&gt;
with (at least) the following in the commit message:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This closes #3727&lt;/p&gt;

